CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 3, 1959, pg. 15 reads: "Party-Goers - These young people are some of the many guests who attended the party held at Timmie Williams home, 3300 Iowa St., Dec. 27. Mr. Williams is shown in upper photo near his high fidelity machine.  Some of the others shown in the upper photo are Antoinette McTurner, Norma Pettigrew, Karen West, Bea Bedell, Erlene Adair, Donna Rideout, Bob Worthington, Alan James and Roger Thomas.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of young men and women, including  Antoinette McTurner, Norma Pettigrew, Karen West, Bea Bedell, Erlene Adair, Donna Rideout, Bob Worthington, Alan James, and Roger Thomas, gathered around Timmie Williams kneeling next to hi-fi, for party in Williams home, 3300 Iowa Street
